						input(type="text", id="txtAbout", name="txtAbout", class="input-large")
					span.help-required *
				.frm-group
					label.control-label.dblock COMPROMISO
					.frm-control
						textarea(type="textarea", id="txtMessage", name="txtMessage", class="txt-large")
					span.help-required *
				p.color-orange.mt20 (*) Campos obligatorios
				.frm-group.row
					button(type="submit", id="sbmSend", class="btn", title="Siguiente") Siguiente